fields.name: DeWalt DCS355N XR Brushless Oscillating Multi-Tool 18V Bare Unit
fields.description: The DeWalt 18V XR Li-ion brushless oscillating multitool is a versatile tool for heavy-duty tasks. Featuring a brushless motor that delivers a no-load speed of 20,000 Opm, it offers faster completion of the most demanding applications. The dual-grip variable speed trigger provides greater control and adjustment of speed during use. A bright LED light illuminates the working area, making it ideal when working in poorly lit spaces. With the universal accessory adaptor, you can use this tool with most oscillating tool accessory brands. The tool comes with a set of accessories, including a sanding pad, 29 sheets of assorted sandpaper, 31 x 43mm wood with nails blade and 31 x 43mm fast cut wood blade and also universal blade adaptor so that you can start your project straight away.The tool comes as bare unit and the battery or charger are not included.
